k: break-word;" role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" id="contentregion" locked="0">                                       <tr>                     <td class="contentbuilder-html" style="padding: 0;">                      <div style="color: #0e1e0f;font-family: 'Avenir Next', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';font-size: 18px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 28px;margin: 0 auto;">                       <p><strong><em><u style="background-color: #FFFF00">[ADD CORRECT NAMES AND DELETE THIS PROMPT] </u></em></strong><br />Hi <span style="background-color: #FFFF00">{CLIENT 1 NAME} &amp; {CLIENT 2 NAME}</span>,</p>                       <p>Your advice documents are now available in the portal. Here you will find a folder containing the following:</p><strong><em><u><p style="background-color: #FFFF00">[AMEND LIST BELOW AS NECESSARY AND DELETE THIS PROMPT]</p></u></em></strong>                       <ul>                        <li>A recording of your meeting</li>                        <li>A copy of the presentation, including important risk warnings and appendices that contain important additional details</li>                        <li>Personalised illustrations for your recommended NOVA products</li>                        <li>Relevant <span style="background-color: #FFFF00">[PROVIDER]</span> product brochures</li>                        <li>Passive Plus portfolio Key Investor Information Documents (KIIDs)<span style="background-color: #FFFF00"> [REVIEW IF NECESSARY]</span></li>                       </ul>                       <p><a href="https://portal.novawm.com/documents">Access your document store</a> using your existing email and password. You can also navigate there from the portal menu.</p>                       <p>We will notify you whenever important documents are added to the portal.</p><strong><em><u><span style="background-color: #FFFF00">[ONLY IF ACCEPTANCE IS STILL REQUIRED] </span></u></em></strong>                       <p><strong>Next Steps</strong><br /><span style="background-color: #FFFF00">{CLIENT 2 NAME}</span>, as you didn't take part in the meeting it is important you review the details of our advice, including watching the meeting recording, and confirm whether you are happy to go ahead. A simple reply to this email will suffice.</p>                       <p>If you need anything explained in more detail or have any questions, we will be happy to answer these. You can book a meeting with <span style="background-color: #FFFF00">{PARTNER NAME}</span>.</p>                       <p><span style="background-color: #FFFF00">[ADD HYPERLINK TO THE WORDS <em>"book a meeting with {partner name} AND DELETE THIS PROMPT"</em>]</span></p>                      </div></td>                    </tr>                                     </table></td>                </tr>                                              <tr>                 <td>                  <table style="font-size:14px; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; word-break: break-word;" role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" id="contentregion" locked="1">                                       <tr>                     <td class="contentbuilder-html" style="padding: 0;">                      <div style="color: #0e1e0f;font-family: 'Avenir Next', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';font-size: 18px;font-weight: 400;line-height: 28px;margin: 0 auto;">                       <p>Kind regards</p>                       <p>Amy Farringdon</p>                       <p><a href="tel:+442073900222">+44 (020) 7390 0222</a> | <a href="mailto:amy@nvoawm.com">amy@novawm.com</a> | <a href="https://novawm.com/">Web</a></p><em><p>The information in this email is intended solely for the recipient. Access, copying or re-use of information in it by anyone else